Winter. This is my watch;
Charles Heley
, London, No. 1711; it is now without a glass, it was whole when it was in my room.

DANIEL CARTWRIGHT sworn. - I am a City officer: On the 28th of this month, I was upon duty in Smithfield-market, I was called to take the prisoner into custody, he was sitting at the Belltap; I was charged with the prisoner, and three pigs; I delivered the pigs to the prosecutor by order of the Magistrates at Worship-street; the pigs were shewn to Saunders in the prisoner's presence; the prisoner said he was sorry for what he had done, it was all through a woman;
John Read
was with me.
